
  **********************************************************************

    PureBasic 2.00 - Main Update Pack

    Update:   Major (new compiler, new commands)
    Released: 17/01/2001

  **********************************************************************


     Dear PureBasic user,


  This package will update PureBasic 1.xx to 2.00. You need to have any
  PureBasic 1.xx full version correctly installed on your hard disk.


  Installation:
  -------------

  Use the supplied install script, select your langage and select the
  drawer where PureBasic is installed (theorically 'PureBasic:')

  Once the install script has finish its job, just launch PureBasic
  and check the title bar to see if the update has been performed
  ('PureBasic 2.00' should be visible).

  You may install a langage pack if you need it. Following langages
  are availables:

    - Francais
    - Deutsch
    - Russian

  Don't forget to check the history file in the PureBasic.guide to
  see the changes !


      Thank you,

          The Fantaisie Software Team



